# Tests

- Prefer descriptive test names (`MethodName_Scenario_Expected`).
- Use the same layering rules as production code: tests target public API surfaces (controllers, handlers) or isolated units without reaching across layers incorrectly.
- Avoid flaky timing; use `CancellationToken`/`WaitAsync` patterns consistent with the codebase.
